象&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;美国最高法院&lt;/strong&gt;屏蔽了美联储免受特朗普的努力&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/Wt0wXNKF4qglNMjg5_cGVAkdE81n9k33VKJWMIWv2G4TVm1GbSjPtPqLqoNGV3CjR-NHQgKz345y3Opron_DPvqytUHJ9Io3yMveZEG9_knE_JPWYJLlLztx3bn1st77MAdAXDjdvQ1QnHRoLI9D2A4YnyyaoHxRmujhtfc1lGk-oV5RfCRk-e0F1PwfTS1i74c0rcD7OPPi_XZ-ZpkisZEUFGNoRTIAPLik6Eg2rkpSRsIWOP50ftwlsYGxfgseyGXvbp9OI_8cK1-nA78Go_Fw1w/rPiimg29_GmEwY4d46lvks0J38R5EjoB/9" target="_blank"&gt;解雇高级政府官员&lt;/a&gt;。在周四的一项裁决中，特朗普罢免了另外两个机构的领导人，法院表示，其裁决&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/zL1FMRSmlXzDq9F72bAD-N3N7eH0WenjG2eiouaPU6290dmYdlS8gVk2j3CCVGxW8Yg905X9pBmw9Edtp-ytU0PoGMtTDTM-LeOO60NO281r1MwMcC-NyKxn3DJJ6YSAoNRYa2hbzBgkYk_HgthIhfs9JzkifwrYuTo71qodtemtRBVYCLsGoH6WqZQBabOg6KAI7BYCrrKA2PwWXHW1dULw4eIYKOphDrVPTiodXyCZMTSlGJRMVrMpTw3YYiiSYsfieeQuZ7pi_rN_l3RE3O8_AQ/Bq3BmkxgVisH0kojFFG_EouZ6143dXRg/9" target="_blank"&gt;将不适用于美联储&lt;/a&gt;，称其为“独特的，准私人的实体”。 &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/MXaGaHDK2Vzrt5jA-D8whYjQNS44tvhbYId_DITXGCceyDRpoFVquwIYCojSCOm8eXln7iB3lhH1R8vfvdsapRbQKChIu_RY7S01vYqYRusIKFJw_3OXjFDYkKgvxfBvWl9-JpLfGtutu6tHqkpqzuRuF7lJB4U5DDmEHnGsoWMD-SEFvF5UekQJHCDQRJH62-na0LSlkOV9TdSLEb4i1LIqVJxeOOgUp0HbL6POMQi4bgE-p8tcZoDnmvDYi66vOTWM-0oF0QEOoUYjsJu6kkAzYA/61eXlfqIfWSAq2Dalnm9N-OjWHRGsLYa/9" target="_blank"&gt;杰罗姆·鲍威尔（Jerome Powell）的好消息&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;餐饮不是很好。&lt;/strong&gt;昨晚， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/iRLCn7hvBqI7RrcHqTBQR7j8JHbVP2ZN_KIJGwL9_r2nOCx5cf6xT19n56Yjf7zuvQ_FWDQUu0392oEUvuNifHqS395nTPhm888SSoqTsAPw-l29ubwyG8Ru1BZ-1_k5PO_LP0X7X7dHS5Q-IO1z-5bc7kReW69QAglS2LWLrkBYjdqbcr_VU1h2VBE6sEWiJJFUS7WZyQ07zyPJuAwrnJ7mA560CUqy8R3SujD3CaewmAN7BevS24pnvzKEXpPed3hcu89NYPzAxClNBahzLa9uJA/6scAcXaQclfVz4fBwa28gaGXCKLc1213/9" target="_blank"&gt;特朗普硬币持有者被邀请在特朗普的华盛顿高尔夫俱乐部用餐&lt;/a&gt;，他们在那里吃了菲利特·米尼翁（Filet Mignon），并向抗议者大喊：“羞耻！”据一位有些失望的与会者说，总统发表了演讲，离开了。那些在那里的人&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/7xDRpwddXn4l2RFYgv0C98fziV8cS3dvhTbkvD7L2xQzZyVLzJDrnniDXO4ONkcQW8J9sZPfFLR0vzCwpI9RUm5kKQ3-Hv5q_rdeNOJJmGQDlTABdLzvH-Esj7M1PYS9PEpPSH9Mcqli0sCHlvhyzY7eeB2kKIj0TBUFQ7nRzr1D1M5U5AhbRubUjwXV9VM45ikgZLbUPK6S_UMCUKnNO4Lr0RZm3KV07-VnM9JRMXH16Mgd9o1UvjV3ER1kbFF3gdVitPbnyAY6QPqgw-PCVcQeHg/WNz4j7KMT3TO4jqtU2pA9MF0PHPdZtTg/9" target="_blank"&gt;包括中国企业家贾斯汀·孙（Justin Sun）&lt;/a&gt;和一名男子，他们仅以1200美元的价格就坐了座位。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/qtlcll7AMHdUV9KfJBqI9f9HtpnQQNKitbpWNNiRyvIRsobdRI-EvXZaJL95p1eKp2YenUd2X_QX05D4t4V3r_u-j3PpTtSJE1bMmHcRd20CG7PV4Y_9NpmfkqNZn2eNT8d6n_E9tOZrVvznGjAUCsjets_k4EqzXzW7QnycCbyPq9d6aN5GltC2dPhEO_2AlbkGU1tQqMJOMn3LY_DGkYNKIxINQ9qACMXr_kvoAk_FxidCQiwcMPXnOF0HRWBbEG76mmqbTsw8AfkaKWxqsh9byw/b1LlITvMhHUzJ88frh8BHQlWn2P9r2Y9/9" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iT.240bhhLjA/v0/-1x-1.png" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="alt" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iT.240bhhLjA/v0/-1x-1.png" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" width="530" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;一名芝加哥男子&lt;/strong&gt;被指控杀害华盛顿特区的两名以色列大使馆工作人员，首次出庭，并被&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/2GeAbOMSnZaz2T9ULe8qHHtZi_2qUAFeRZ0vInpDH_fhF5dorx75WLu3atRq_3gxtDwjDauLSH44SEPucV4hc3XGznry6O0R4qBQvXebT2mMIJd_FsnRXnA_6OnoHs-geQPVPp7k8isXU5mm8MzObVLh-h4ogKuOAFRNEafDO4r2_x1nWjLEaD-CoHwN51c_4qZh-YJIO9